"AM" 9.9 - clone configurations and relocate AppMan apps (#1818)

* Add option to clone/read the/a list of apps installed/to install

see https://github.com/ivan-hc/AM/issues/1817#issuecomment-3303621541

* Option "clone" with "-i"  flag installs apps from a list

...now you can clone other's configurations, including apps installed locally and system-wide in AM

* List apps to clone by separating local apps from system apps

* Draft new option "relocate"

* Option "clone -i", add a confirmation prompt to install the listed apps

* Add option "relocate", to reinstall AppMan apps to a new location
